The main script to run the ASR training and tests is run.sh

Please set the KALDI_PATH in path.sh to a pre-installed latest kaldi checkout rootpath.
SRILM is to be installed in tools/
steps and utils are softlinks to be made to KALDI_PATH/egs/wsj/s5/{steps,utils}

cmd.sh is customized for training on isolated servers (Non-grid)
The nnet training script towards the bottom of run.sh is recommeded to be run on CUDA-ENABLED GPU. Kaldi also to be configured to use CUDA LIBS.
